title: The Power of Vulnerability Pt.1
itunes:title: The Power of Vulnerability Pt.1
description:
Episode 482 - Vulnerability is a strange thing. It is hard for us to be vulnerable and to open ourselves up to other people, yet it is the only thing that can build deep relationships. In this two part episode, I dive into the power of vulnerability and talk about why we need to learn to be more vulnerable.
